            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%BA%AB%E4%BD%93%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E5%BC%82%E5%B8%B8%E6%98%AF%E8%82%9D%E8%84%8F%E5%9C%A8%E9%A2%84%E8%AD%A6%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%BA%AB%E4%BD%93%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E5%BC%82%E5%B8%B8%E6%98%AF%E8%82%9D%E8%84%8F%E5%9C%A8%E9%A2%84%E8%AD%A6%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#身体出现哪些异常是肝脏在预警#</span></a>】据统计，我国约有4亿人有或轻或重的肝部问题，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%82%9D%E8%84%8F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%E5%8F%91%E7%97%85%E6%97%A9%E6%9C%9F%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E5%BE%88%E9%9A%BE%E5%AF%9F%E8%A7%89%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%82%9D%E8%84%8F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%E5%8F%91%E7%97%85%E6%97%A9%E6%9C%9F%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E5%BE%88%E9%9A%BE%E5%AF%9F%E8%A7%89%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#肝脏疾病发病早期一般很难察觉#</span></a>，只有体检才能发现轻度的、早期的肝脏病变。医生提醒，有这些症状要警惕：①跟平时相比明显感觉疲惫；②右上腹出现胀痛，并伴有轻度厌食、腹泻等情况。日常生活中，如何预防肝脏疾病？看👇🏻 <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4880549639290951" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hc3oi5ac4jj61gj0tk4qp02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/B0WGOXRxlx083XqsftHW01041200VOb50E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1679304189&amp;ssig=7TU%2Fua2V9a&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/gsGq6kzVlx083XqrQe2401041200uxyk0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1679304189&amp;ssig=x4VvboRzVM&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/PxEdtRu3lx083XqrrkCs01041200jABL0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1679304189&amp;ssig=ENjo8CBiIW&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4880549639290951&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
